Package: datathin
Title: Splitting a random variable into independent training and test components 
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Anna", "Neufeld", , "aneufeld@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ameer", "Dharamshi", , "adharams@uw.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: Implements the data thinning methodology from the papers "Data thinning for convolution-closed distributions" (Neufeld et al., 2023) and "Generalized Data Thinning Using Sufficient Statistics" (Dharamshi et al., 2023). 
